"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"质押网站：\\n\\n[https://portal.astar.network/#/store/discover-dapps](https://portal.astar.network/#/store/discover-dapps)\\n\\n### 1.安装polkadot.js插件\\n\\n[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/polkadot%7Bjs%7D-extension/mopnmbcafieddcagagdcbnhejhlodfdd](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/polkadot%7Bjs%7D-extension/mopnmbcafieddcagagdcbnhejhlodfdd)\\n\\n### 2.设置polkadot.js钱包\\n\\n这部和小狐狸差不多，我就不详细介绍了，保存好私钥和json文件\\n\\n### 3.配置polkadot.js钱包\\n\\n如下图所示\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nrytosMQtmJJ_F_6zYRQf.png?height=1661&width=1109)\\n\\n此步找不到shiden网络的请按照如下方式操作：\\n\\n> 打开链接：\\n\\n[https://polkadot.js.org/apps/?rpc=wss%3A%2F%2Fshiden.api.onfinality.io%2Fpublic-ws#/settings/metadata](https://polkadot.js.org/apps/?rpc=wss%3A%2F%2Fshiden.api.onfinality.io%2Fpublic-ws#/settings/metadata)\\n\\n> 用json导入钱包\\n>\\n> 左上角切换kusama-shiden\\n>\\n> 设置-元数据-更新元数据\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5z_9xeqaT9LZbDggj5LEw.png?height=1339&width=3000)\\n\\n> 完成以上步骤，回到插件切换shiden网络\\n\\n### 4.转入余额\\n\\n> 如果余额在小狐狸，请按照下面链接指引转入波卡钱包\\n>\\n> [medium.com/@bitcoinzhang?p=cbd353684fd3me](http://medium.com/@bitcoinzhang?p=cbd353684fd3me)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/0x410a0887cC91cCf1e8Db56422b9a5D8B078c2200/VmDKg0NcdH0clOMzBWcVV3BsteS8Hjo4GjlC93A_rP4](https://mirror.xyz/0x410a0887cC91cCf1e8Db56422b9a5D8B078c2200/VmDKg0NcdH0clOMzBWcVV3BsteS8Hjo4GjlC93A_rP4)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/@bitcoinzhang?p=cbd353684fd3me](https://medium.com/@bitcoinzhang?p=cbd353684fd3me)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/0x410a0887cC91cCf1e8Db56422b9a5D8B078c2200/VmDKg0NcdH0clOMzBWcVV3BsteS8Hjo4GjlC93A_rP4](https://mirror.xyz/0x410a0887cC91cCf1e8Db56422b9a5D8B078c2200/VmDKg0NcdH0clOMzBWcVV3BsteS8Hjo4GjlC93A_rP4)\\n\\n> 如果余额在交易所，直接从交易所转账到波卡钱包即可（记住先小额测试，确认没问题再进行大额转账\\n\\n### 5.进行质押\\n\\n打开质押网站\\n\\n[https://portal.astar.network/#/balance/balance-plasm](https://portal.astar.network/#/balance/balance-plasm)\\n\\n链接polka.js钱包，，选择有余额的钱包\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2MLUYqd-Or8janBWGW541.png?height=1201&width=2002)\\n\\n然后你就可以选择dapp质押了\",\"timestamp\":1634149928,\"title\":\"如何参与Shiden质押\"},\"digest\":\"KwxqpBMe0623zQgGQ9hRQvcjwXQG6olby5urV68t0e8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x410a0887cC91cCf1e8Db56422b9a5D8B078c2200\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"or8IlElCbNFA-ME4JISWhy3CUn6hxmzHqtsrvMUJjME\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"HUsW3tIsdaqB9Omo29H6iIhPnq7APG4ftEFYd-h4B9k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"zsZTPaijbjGWS_GMCxdbpK3St33s873K0AccCuiI_jJou8L21owWK2IlraJNRkPYQ4r0P8D--wuwSmMzKjJjrw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x7cd404b476989143c5993571a6ffcdf5329a09997be0dd002d7783dad1dcce653f4224136582b7723fb0594b6fd1ce39dd629be78a1cfc662cb940cdfe3a1adc1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"or8IlElCbNFA-ME4JISWhy3CUn6hxmzHqtsrvMUJjME\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"HUsW3tIsdaqB9Omo29H6iIhPnq7APG4ftEFYd-h4B9k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"WKsAnS1SgFvEsEBo1wJ2s1keAhWGCnBe4wIabdgMMjg\"}"